    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Single player horror where you must wait out the night while supernatural entities make their way ever closer.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A chance at freedom</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jumping at the opportunity to be a free man, &quot;no strings attached&quot;. You take up an offer that the warden gave to all lifers. Seven nights in some dilapidated storehouse? sounded easy enough. Now you sit in a barely lit room waiting for further instruction.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Too late to turn back now</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alone &amp; shackled to a chair. You're armed with a flash bulb from an old camera, a thee-position switch for some shutter doors, &amp; a CCTV feed. The objective is simple...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survive until morning and KEEP THEM OUT.</strong></p>",
